<P>PRAELATICUS TRIUMPHATUS. A Vindication of <HI>Presbyterial Ordination &amp; Government.</HI> In An&s;wer to <HI>The Scripture-Bi&s;hop Examin'd,</HI> And to <HI>Eleutherius Enervatus.</HI></P>
